snippet.title: Meet Kapil Sharma | Episode 90
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer of Kapil Sharma movie at:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xtd1aB-iLe0&t=52s

Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com

#kapilsharma #sandeepmaheshwari

In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Exploring Amritsar With Kapil Sharma | Tere Gully Mein EP 36 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
On this episode of Tera Gully Mein, we met Kapil Sharma and had a trip down memory lane in Amritsar. From binging on buttery Amritsari Kulchas to devouring some divine Amritsari Kulfa, Kamiya and Kapil experienced a food coma in Amritsar. 

Kapil also showed us around his Amritsar home and the theatre he previously worked at. He spoke to us about his childhood, his struggling journey, his battle with depression, his marriage life, the upcoming film Zwigato and much more. 

Kamiya Jani & Kapil Sharma had a phenomenal time exploring Amritsar. Hope you enjoy the video too!

Kamiya Jani & Kapil Sharma had a phenomenal time exploring Amritsar. Hope you enjoy the video too!

snippet.description:

Tere Bin Episode 25 Teaser - 16th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

Lyrics:
Mahol pura lor ch aa jawani wale jor ch aa
Akh puri lal kude jhotte aali tor ch aa
Ni munda puri tohar ch aa
Daure paunda daur ch aa
Jhanjar to vadhke khadaka 32 bor ch aa
Saman peya khideya ni sikhar dupehar ch aa
Jatt tere shehar ch ni jatt tere shehar ch aa
Jatt tere shehar ch ni jatt tere shehar ch aa

Kanna vich nattiya te gallan kare tattiya 
Gaddi lali side te jagake dine battiya 
Battiya jagawe kade battiya nu band kre
Sade nalo vadh talk dub wala sandh kre 
Set kithe hunde laan te oh pinde chhanke
Chali goli janke oh bni pyi aa jaan te 
Khade hikk tanke 
Lde jihde kand sanu mile sala aanke
Jutti paai kadmi jamana sade pair ch 
Jatt tere shehar ch ni jatt tere shehar ch aa
Jatt tere shehar ch ni jatt tere shehar ch aa

Punjab ude pura aisa laya pill
Shehar tere jatt aaya aake mil
Buffer kare burrrr burrr
Mumbai ka shotgun
Driving seat pe dekh kon - Jassie Gill
Black car lekin kale mere dhande nahi
Beat karun kill maru mai bande nahi 
Pange lenge bande toh cheer denge pura
Punjab ke sher maare panje nahi 
Kabu me rakh apni yeh kali zulfon ko
Bekabu kar rakha tune yahan ladkon ko
Bawal kam nhi tera pure shehar me
Ab ladwake manegi kya mulkon ko
Tu dikhti kehar mai bhi likhta zehar
Mujhe pta meri shayari tu karti hai share
Jhoome sara sara din jab baje mere gaane
Nachane sabko jatt aaya tere shehar

Nature ne kabbe vairi mudke ni labhe 
Notice ch mere ki hai hunda sajje khabbe 
Khabbe hath ghadi hundi saje hath kadha ni
Jithe munda khadje madan hoje rarha ni
Mukhde te sang ni chedu koi jang ni
Shankdi wang ni tu utto gyi khang ni
Rehge munde dang ni 
Sare sidhe krne main sire de malang ni
Gill Rony kathe kude ajj full lehar ch aa
Jatt tere shehar ch ni jatt tere shehar ch aa
Jatt tere shehar ch ni jatt tere shehar ch aa

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3721 - 17 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3721: Tapu Sena Ka Nimantran
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu Sena has been secretly planning and working on their idea at the clubhouse after they were advised to get serious about their career and future goals. Tapu Snea invites all the members of the Gokuldham society to the clubhouse to announce their idea. They also request Bhide to right the invitation on the notice board as well as of inviting the residents at 8:30. Everyone starts speculating about the idea of Tapu Sena, Bagha and Nattu Kaaka also ask Jethalal to end their shift before 8:30 as they are also invited in the gathering. Watch the episode.  

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3721, 17 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000213921

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Hello friends, today, on 18 march 2023 Saturday, I am presenting to you all the  Papmochani Ekadashi vrat katha of Chaitra Krishna Paksha Ekadashi . Papmochani Ekadashi  means Ekadashi which destroys sins. Keeping fast on the day of Papmochani Ekadashi results in salvation along with the elimination of all sins. Papmochani Ekadashi comes before Chaitra Navratri. On this day, Chaturbhuji form of Lord Vishnu is worshiped by law and we must listen Ekadashi vrat katha. 

According to Papmochani Ekadashi ki katha kahani, Yudhishthira asked - Lord Krishna! Now please explain the great significance of Ekadashi of Chaitra Krishna Paksha. Hey Madhusudan! What is the name of this Ekadashi? Which god is worshiped in this and what is the law of this fast? Lord Shri Krishna said - Rajendra! Ekadashi of Krishna Paksha of Chaitra month is called Papamochini Ekadashi. Many sins of humans are destroyed due to the effect of his fast. I will tell you the story of this fastthe meritorious sages and Apsara Manjugosha lost track of time and indulged in love for 57 years. When sage regained consciousness, he repented of the sin he had committed. After  Papmochani Ekadashi vrat, the meritorious sage got rid of sin and he again got into austerities. Apsara Manjughosha got rid of vampire vagina by fasting Papmochani Ekadashi and she went to the heavenly world wearing a divine body. The best man who observes Papmochani Ekadashi and listens Ekadashi ki kahani all his sins are destroyed. By reading and listening #Ekadashivratkatha, one gets the fruit of the donation 1000 cows.  Papmochani ekadashi fast is very pious.
In video of Papmochini ekadashi katha, Lord krishna is telling significance and importance of papmochani ekadashi vrat. people who perform papmochani ekadashi vrat, they get rid from all of their sins no matter how big their sins were. Lord Vishnu bless that person and take him to vaikuntha dham in the end.
Papmochani Ekadashi Saturday, March 18, 2023

Hello friends, today, on 18 march 2023 Saturday, I am presenting to you all the  Papmochani Ekadashi vrat katha of Chaitra Krishna Paksha Ekadashi . Papmochani Ekadashi  means Ekadashi which destroys sins. Keeping fast on the day of Papmochani Ekadashi results in salvation along with the elimination of all sins. Papmochani Ekadashi comes before Chaitra Navratri. On this day, Chaturbhuji form of Lord Vishnu is worshiped by law and we must listen Ekadashi vrat katha. 

According to Papmochani Ekadashi ki katha kahani, Yudhishthira asked - Lord Krishna! Now please explain the great significance of Ekadashi of Chaitra Krishna Paksha. Hey Madhusudan! What is the name of this Ekadashi? Which god is worshiped in this and what is the law of this fast? Lord Shri Krishna said - Rajendra! Ekadashi of Krishna Paksha of Chaitra month is called Papamochini Ekadashi. Many sins of humans are destroyed due to the effect of his fast. I will tell you the story of this fastthe meritorious sages and Apsara Manjugosha lost track of time and indulged in love for 57 years. When sage regained consciousness, he repented of the sin he had committed. After  Papmochani Ekadashi vrat, the meritorious sage got rid of sin and he again got into austerities. Apsara Manjughosha got rid of vampire vagina by fasting Papmochani Ekadashi and she went to the heavenly world wearing a divine body. The best man who observes Papmochani Ekadashi and listens Ekadashi ki kahani all his sins are destroyed. By reading and listening #Ekadashivratkatha, one gets the fruit of the donation 1000 cows.  Papmochani ekadashi fast is very pious.
In video of Papmochini ekadashi katha, Lord krishna is telling significance and importance of papmochani ekadashi vrat. people who perform papmochani ekadashi vrat, they get rid from all of their sins no matter how big their sins were. Lord Vishnu bless that person and take him to vaikuntha dham in the end.
Papmochani Ekadashi Saturday, March 18, 2023

snippet.description: Rahul Sipligunj and Kaala Bhairava sing their 'RRR' song, 'Naatu Naatu,' in an epic dance number at the 95th Academy Awards. The movie later makes history as it becomes the first Indian feature film to win an Oscar, with the track's composer and lyricist, M.M. Keeravaani and Chandrabose, nabbing Best Original Song. The 2023 Oscars aired on ABC.

snippet.title: Raghavendra Stores - Release Date Announcement | Jaggesh | Santhosh Ananddram | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
Wish a Happy Birthday to the "Navarasa Nayaka Jaggesh" 
Your Humor and talent bring joy to so many.  Here's to another year of laugher and success.  

The Release Date Announcement of "Raghavendra Stores" is finally here!

Raghavendra Stores starring Jaggesh, Directed by Santhosh Ananddram and Produced by Vijay Kiragandur under the Banner of Hombale Films. 

In Theatres 28 April 2023

Movie Details:

Produced by: Vijay Kiragandur

Art : Vishwas Kashyap

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3720 - 16 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3720: Baccho Ka Secret Project
--------------------------------------------------------
At the soda, the Gokuldham men discuss Tapu Sena and their recent activities. Tapu Sena secretly plans to do something to surprise their parents, so they secretly meet at a studio. Jetha asks Taarak about Tapu Sena's plan of action, but Taarak has also failed to retrieve any information. So the Gokuldham men decide to ask Chmpaklal to intervene because he has a good rapport with the kids. When Tapu informs Bhide that Sonu will reach home a bit late, Bhide gets worried and calls the other men; they decide to uncover their secret mission anyhow. Will Tapu Sena's mission be unveiled finally?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3720, 16 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

#kannanbhagavathy #pregnancy #familyvlog 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3719 - 15 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3719: Tapu Sena's New Mission
--------------------------------------------------------
The parents are worried for their kids' future. They catch them hanging out at the clubhouse and ask them questions. They are worried that the Tapu Sena is not serious about their lives and careers. Tapu Sena tries to make them understand. Taarak decides to have a talk with them without the parents. He makes them understand their parents' point of view as well. Tapu Sena decided and promises that they will think of something. They discuss it amongst themselves and try to come up with a solution. 

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3719, 15 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000213651
